TITLE: Implementing a Configurable Payload Plugin Factory (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Factory function for building a configurable Payload CMS plugin in TypeScript. Accepts plugin-specific options, clones and extends incoming config, modifies arrays with spread syntax, and extends lifecycle hooks. Requires TypeScript and payload types. Inputs: pluginOptions, incomingConfig; Output: modified config for Payload CMS.
