SOURCE: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/packages/db-sqlite/README.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { buildConfig } from 'payload/config'
import { sqliteAdapter } from '@payloadcms/db-sqlite'

export default buildConfig({
  db: sqliteAdapter({
    client: {
      url: process.env.DATABASE_URI,
    },
  }),
  // ...rest of config
})
```

