TITLE: Calling Stripe API via Payload Plugin Proxy (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code provides an alternative way to interact with the Stripe API using the 'stripeProxy' utility from '@payloadcms/plugin-stripe'. It wraps Stripe API calls for use within Payload projects, passing necessary parameters (including the secret key, method, and arguments) and demonstrates best practices for handling both success and error states based on HTTP status codes. Requires the Payload plugin-stripe package, environment variables, and correct plugin setup.
